hercules is a 2014 american 3d action fantasy adventure film directed by brett ratner , written by ryan j. condal and evan spiliotopoulos and starring dwayne johnson , ian mcshane , rufus sewell and john hurt .   it is based on the graphic novel hercules : the thracian wars .   distributed jointly by paramount pictures and metro-goldwyn-mayer , it was released on july 25 , 2014 .   it is one of two hollywood-studio hercules films released in 2014 , the other one being lionsgate 's the legend of hercules .   the film became a box office success earning $ 244 million on a $ 100 million budget and received mixed reviews from critics , who , however , praised the action sequences and johnson 's acting .   hercules was released on blu-ray 3d , blu-ray and dvd on november 4 , 2014 by paramount home media distribution .